ooc: the 2 bots see hot rod and prowl and their jaws drop. they immediately 
drop to one knee and begin acting very humble.

ghost: Oh primus! Sir, I...I'm ghost, and this is my friend goth!
goth: It is an unspeakable honor meeting you, mr. prime. it's good to see 
another autobot here.
ghost: just to avoid confusion, despite being a car, i'm a maximal. it's a 
long story, and it's why we got shot here. Commander prowl, would you like to 
go back and salvage some of our craft.

--part1_8a.12cab908.297dfd52_boundary
